==Finnish==

===Etymology===

From ''linnun'' (genitive of [[lintu]]) + [[rata#Finnish|rata]]. Literally ''bird's track'' or ''bird's way''.

===Proper noun===
'''Linnunrata'''

#the [[Milky Way]] galaxy

===Noun===
'''linnunrata'''

#[[Milky Way]], the diffuse band of light that streches across the sky
#a [[galaxy]]

====Synonyms====
*(''galaxy'') [[galaksi]]

